{"id": "1250120736509657241", "channel_id": "1250120736509657241", "type": 0, "author_id": "908474139583602740", "author_name": "jester_romut", "author_bot": false, "content": "我患了不聽游戲原聲就畫不出同人的病", "timestamp": "2024-06-11T16:13:29.704000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1250120736509657241", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "這游戲有沒有ost啊", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1250131757353668679", "channel_id": "1250131757353668679", "type": 0, "author_id": "1002938431271358494", "author_name": "1027vliaji", "author_bot": false, "content": "就是这期融灾第3关，有一个和猫猫赌黑印的事件，这种随机事件和用融灾商店凹造物一起出现不太好。\n有时候开局商店是好造物，但是赌黑印失败了，会很难受，下次用这个地图还是别加这样的事件了，来个白银变黄金的事件谢谢<:finger:1234798285466632212>", "timestamp": "2024-06-11T16:57:17.278000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1250131757353668679", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于融灾事件的随机性的建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1250127515842904115", "channel_id": "1250127515842904115", "type": 0, "author_id": "1002938431271358494", "author_name": "1027vliaji", "author_bot": false, "content": "这是一个奇怪到我觉自己被小丑头追杀的bug。\n\n首先我用借来的24打了融灾3-3，小丑头标记给了24的【纷乱切割】，然后【纷乱切割】被标记为【打击】，好了，我打完了。\n\n然后我用自己的24打了莉莉的活动，商店买了一个【残缺面孔】，接着【纷乱切割】也和打击防御一样【+1算力】，变成【4算力】了。\n\n然后拉蒙娜大招抓出来的【纷乱切割】切割甚至还有【1算力】！😅 \n\n另外【纷乱切割】打出后，不享受【残缺面孔】给的【+35狂气】。\n\n后面用【须臾的火】复制了一张【纷乱切割】，还是【4算力】。本来事情已经结束了。接着来了个【诅咒石碑】换掉了【残缺面孔】，【纷乱切割】果然变回正常的【3算力】。\n\n（如果今晚我被子里看见小丑头，罚校猫三个月没有猫粮）", "timestamp": "2024-06-11T16:40:26.023000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-11T16:45:20.290000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1250127516404813955", "filename": "QQ20240612002441.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1642597, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1250127515842904115/1250127516404813955/QQ20240612002441.png?ex=6a00b4fa&is=69ff637a&hm=ec2ea034b81231031d70028b9a86797a3a6eec4f63e148292d714fbc0b6f2205&"}, {"id": "1250127516933423155", "filename": "QQ20240612001836.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1754698, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1250127515842904115/1250127516933423155/QQ20240612001836.png?ex=6a00b4fa&is=69ff637a&hm=cbe49ee5302b2a1d9df505ee2606a284309d81725eb3f9f317274793196a7c0a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1250127515842904115", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」24技能【纷乱切割】与【残缺面孔】以及【小丑头】的算力bug。", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1250047746325348424", "channel_id": "1250047746325348424", "type": 0, "author_id": "1189791024424431627", "author_name": "vivivispray", "author_bot": false, "content": "如题，现在越来越多的卡组是带衍生卡的，比如羊妈，手牌多的时候卡与卡之间的间距就变得很小，出牌的时候需要去抠，打快了还容易错。错了还没有回退（话说回合回退打算什么时候出来\n所以建议在多卡牌的时候加一个展开的机制去避免这个问题。\n以上", "timestamp": "2024-06-11T11:23:27.488000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1250047746325348424", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」手牌展开真的很有必要", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
